precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1991-2502, which authorized for the
borrowing by the issue and sale of Treasury bills or Treasury notes for
the payment of Treasury bills or other securities in the JANUARY 1, 1992
to MARCH 31, 1992 period, INCREASING THE AMOUNT AUTHORIZED TO BE BORROWED.
